name: All the world's a stage V2

metadata.name: Givi
metadata.description:
Bright Givi from sunny Georgia. 
«And all the men and women merely players:
They have their exits and their entrances;
And one man in his time plays many parts,
His acts being seven ages....»
Heroes of eras, films and legends are simple street passers-by of everyday life.
Popular and unknown.
Fictional and real.
Funny and serious.
Talented and mediocre.
Passers-by of our lives always look like someone.
